tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All measured parameters are within normal limits except for a mildly elevated HbA1c (6.1%), indicating impaired glucose metabolism or prediabetes. Renal function, electrolytes, and glucose are normal. Recommend follow-up for glycemic control and lifestyle modification to prevent progression to diabetes.
